    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        Some things I’m passionate about: AI/ML (from precision health to LLMs), drug discovery (specifically on how we can apply computational biology to redefine therapeutics), the microbiome (I just think it’s super cool) and sewing (I’d include those projects on here too, but there would be no space). 
        <br>
        <br>
        I’m always looking for new opportunities and projects to build my interpersonal skills and apply my current technical skills to improve the lives of those around me. If you’d like to chat, feel free to reach out to aakritil@stanford.edu.
